Class DB2PreparedStatement

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.db2.r2dbc.DB2PreparedStatement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    io.r2dbc.spi.Statement

    public class DB2PreparedStatement
extends Object
implements io.r2dbc.spi.Statement
    Represents a SQL statement to be executed on the database server. Created by a DB2Connection object.
